summary: I had a go at making some dice necklaces! Now my other dice know what happens to dice that misbehave to much. These were really...
caption:
I had a go at making some dice necklaces! Now my other dice know what happens to dice that misbehave to much.

These were really fun to make and I’ll be selling them at a local art fair ^-^

I also noticed after I finished them that I’d accidentally made a Caduceus Clay necklace ^-^ I’m also definitely making a drow to wear one of the iridescent purple ones with.

I’ve also got an ongoing kickstarter to fund a collection of adorable enamel pins. If you’re interested please take a look here:

http://kck.st/2BW0T91
